{"tid":1121251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【再有6.6級地震】馬尼拉唐人街豪宅劇烈搖晃 天台泳池倒水落街","createTime":"2019-04-23T07:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T10:17:17.000Z","uid":65346,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28f2a571e9ae3782af6e78a2087bac595332a958","tid":1121251,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190423/59518617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F59518617&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=0dcd400a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F59518617&h=793affc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190423/59518617</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死人菲律賓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">菲律賓</span>周一下午發生黎克特制6.3級地震，造成至少11死亡，24人失蹤後，今天再發生6.6級地震，傷亡未明。昨天的死傷人數全部來自重災區邦板牙省（Pampanga），首都馬尼拉高樓大廈在事發時激烈搖晃，有豪宅天台泳池池水被搖至傾瀉而下。<br />\n邦板牙省受災最嚴重，波拉克市（Porac）一幢4層高建築物倒塌，救援人員在現場用起重機和手提鑽挖掘，當地州長表示：「救援人員至少仍然聽到一個人還活着，那個人被埋在石屎土板下。」幾間有幾世紀歷史的教堂亦在地震中受損。<br />\n在馬尼拉商業區，有建築物搖晃，民眾需要疏散到戶外。網民分享短片，地震發生時整座大廈搖晃，頂部不斷有灰塵掉下；來自倫敦的網民「Majick」分享的影片可見，位於唐人街、樓高181米的豪華公寓大樓「Anchor Skysuites」，在地震中不斷搖晃，天台泳池池水傾瀉而下儼如瀑布，他寫道：「地震很強，就連天台的泳池都倒水了。」<br />\n住在馬尼拉的武術教練胡斯托（Dani Justo）表示，地震時她在家中，她憶述：「晾起的衣服搖動得非常強，我的西施犬也跌在地上。」<br />\n菲律賓位處俗稱「火環」（Ring of Fire）的環太平洋地震帶，該區火山和地震活動頻繁，新西蘭、印尼、台灣、日本、阿拉斯加、美國西岸、墨西哥、厄瓜多爾、智利等地，都位處這個圍繞太平洋、長達四萬公里的板塊運動活躍區域。"},{"pid":"75b9cc6b924d89f4ba25b11121cad4e487b722a6","tid":1121251,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c24cf37f4a9605a7730d72ab6f7a962d9e6428e","tid":1121251,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e5b4901dd04feca31477adc23a323f07e661495","tid":1121251,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"琴日講完會再震咁快又震<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一條地震帶好似係<br />\n照之前預言家講下次到印尼應該<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/db/Quake_epicenters_1963-98.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fdb%2FQuake_epicenters_1963-98.png&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b1009b3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/db/Quake_epicenters_1963-98.png</a>"},{"pid":"b6e21f617ead9a1b28de63df7b8477bc89094545","tid":1121251,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e5b4901dd04feca31477adc23a323f07e661495","tid":1121251,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"琴日講完會再震咁快又震<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一條地震帶好似係<br />\n照之前預言家講下次到印尼應該<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/db/Quake_epicenters_1963-98.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fdb%2FQuake_epicenters_1963-98.png&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b1009b3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/db/Quake_epicenters_1963-98.png</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://uploa